  "text": "Pure negativity acts as a gravity well pulling all into it. I was wondering first in a social complex whose negativity approaches purity, the pull upon other selves is constant, a positively oriented entity in such a situation would desire for other selves to have their free will, and thusly would find itself removed from its ability to exercise its own free will for the free will of negatively orientities is then upon conquest.",
